<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
  <script type="module" src="/js/index.js" defer></script>
  <title>OPIC 연습용 프로그램</title>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="title-form">
    <div class="title">
      <h1>OPIC 연습용 프로그램</h1>
      <h3>버전: v1.2.0</h3>
      <h3>개발자: 박우림</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="title-footer">
      <a href="https://www.notion.so/Opic-English-Studying-48c6ff419a8b49b299fb62412ddff19d">스크립트 바로가기</a>
      <h4>최종 업데이트 일자: 2021.07.07(수)</h3>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr>

  <section class="main">
    <span class="main-title">원하는 <span class="red">주제</span>와 <span class="red">목소리</span>를 선택해주세요.</span>
    <div class="select-form">
      <article>
        <select>
        </select>
        <select class="voices"></select>
      </article>

      <div class="btn-form">
        <div class="btn speak-btn">Speak Question</div>
        <div class="btn answer-btn">Speak Answer</div>
        <div class="btn pause-btn">Pause Speaking</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="control-form">
    <div class="rate">
      <label for="rate">Rate</label><br><input type="range" min="0" max="2" value="1" step="0.05" id="rate">
      <div class="rate-value">1</div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="pitch">
      <label for="pitch">Pitch</label><br><input type="range" min="0" max="2" value="1" step="0.05" id="pitch">
      <div class="pitch-value">1</div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr>
  
  <article class="script">
    <span class="main-title">Script</span>
    <div class="description"></div>
  </article>
</body>
</html>